      "span_text": "RNA was isolated using RNeasy kit (Qiagen) and cDNA was synthesized using the High Capacity cDNA Reverse Transcription Kit (Applied Biosystems). mRNAs were quantified by qRT-PCR using Taqman Gene expression assays and data analysed by relative quantitation (with standard curves) with normalisation to GAPDH mRNA as previously described [CITATION_1] .",
